{"about_the_game":"Captures is a chess-driven puzzle game. The objective is to capture the opponent's pieces.<br>While the chess pieces move according to the regular rules, the board itself varies from level to level. Boards from 3x3 to 8x8 are present in the game.<br>Also certain squares on the board might have &quot;tile effects&quot;.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712680/extras/curse.gif?t=1629992873\" /> <br>When you capture a piece on a cursed square, you lose your piece as well. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712680/extras/poison.gif?t=1629992873\" /> <br>Pieces that land on a poisoned square will expire in 3 turns.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712680/extras/portal1.gif?t=1629992873\" /> <br>Pieces placed on the portal move to the other portal after black completes its turn.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712680/extras/portal2.gif?t=1629992873\" /> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712680/extras/random.gif?t=1629992873\" /> <br>Pieces that land on a tile with the random effect will transmute into another piece.<br><br><br>The levels are mostly beginner friendly. People who are looking for a challenge can attempt a built-in speedrun. In speedrun mod levels start one after another, and the player has to make fewer than 5 mistakes through out the whole run.<br><br><br><strong>CONTROLS</strong><br><br>-Drag &amp; drop pieces. <br>-Click the restart button or press R key to restart the levels.<br><br><strong>RULES</strong><br><br>-All black pieces must be removed from the board to win the level. <br>-If a stalemate occurs, the level fails.<br>-If white loses all of their pieces the level fails. However, if white loses their last piece at the same time with the black, the level is completed.<br>-During a speed run, reseting a level counts as a mistake.<br><br><br><strong>TIPS</strong><br>-Random tips will be shown through out the game.<br>-CPU likes to trade pieces, take advantage of it!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Baby Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/fa47364ac5fcfee6e2f28d3a95078ae995627354.jpg"},{"name":"Carpenter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/96caab87cc747303f8acfacfc3d3515361bb571e.jpg"},{"name":"Master Carpenter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/2a7149a838ae1b1fa4937cd6ca8f91ea2e021bec.jpg"},{"name":"Outnumbered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/d16cf33676dd4e83f1f04f73d853063c42bb8ca4.jpg"},{"name":"Mix","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/b3b18fb495c0b133986a6fbcb04a9c752a489461.jpg"},{"name":"Mix II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/68d480ebae32ed7a1685f1f942b76e3fcbc9d4e6.jpg"},{"name":"Mix III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/1e44bc12aac7f8dc55e921a0f86826d457262cb2.jpg"},{"name":"Mix IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/fef8de07bf4a72c73701d3d43befc9fce349cce7.jpg"},{"name":"Queen Mastery","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/614c093798882098df889e6b62fa3e125e5853f6.jpg"},{"name":"Rook Mastery","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1712680/29e2dd2eeadeb9aef459ff2e8df06501cd7e1dca.jpg"}],"total":32},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712680/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1629992873","background_